<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">ON THE AGENDA <span class="divider"> | </span></span> The Markit <b>flash services purchasing managersâ index</b> comes out at 9:45 a.m. <b>Microsoft</b> announces quarterly earnings after the market closes. <b>Gary D. Cohn</b>, the president and chief operating officer of Goldman Sachs, is on CNBC at 4:10 p.m.</p>
